    • findByIdAntiquity

      List<PhotoAntiquity> findByIdAntiquity(Integer idAntiquity)
      Retrieves all photos associated with a specific antiquity ID.

      This method queries the database to find all photos linked to the antiquity identified by the given ID. Each photo is returned as a PhotoAntiquity object, which contains information such as the file path and antiquity ID.

      Parameters:
      idAntiquity - the ID of the antiquity whose associated photos are to be retrieved
      Returns:
      a list of PhotoAntiquity objects representing the photos associated with the specified antiquity
      See Also:
      • PhotoAntiquity
